<span style='float: right; width: 280px; height: 187px; margin: 0 0 5px 5px; border: 1px solid black;'><script type='text/javascript'>flash_object ('http://graphics.millsberry.com/buddy/buddy_featured.swf', '280', '187', 'userName=catize&buddyTimeStamp=20070510&buddyScriptURL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.millsberry.com%2Fbuddy%2Fload_buddy_xml.phtml&unixTimeStamp=1179025812&serverTimeOffset=28800', '', 'exactfit', 'transparent');</script></span>
Meet <b>Cateyes</b>, our Citizen of the Week!<br><br>Cateyes hosts tons of parties at her Westridge home and is one of Millsberry's most friendly and social citizens. At <a href='/home/?user=catize'>34459 Shady Court</a>, she treats guests to theme rooms and a diverse music selection including techno and R&B.<br><br>This witty girl first moved to Millsberry on August 6, 2005, and made friends easily because of her sunny outlook and great sense of humor. When you get to know her, you'll see she's also someone who really analyzes situations carefully and is very insightful. She's a great person to ask for advice because she's a flexible and creative thinker.<br><br>When she's not entertaining people at her house, she shops at the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=1">Clothing Store</a> for clothes in her favorite colors&mdash;green, black, and dark blue. She is also a regular after school in the Millsberry Academy <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/academy/lab/">lab</a>, reading up on astronomy, a subject she has recently developed an interest in. Ask her to point out some constellations or explain the phases of the moon&mdash;she loves to share her knowledge!<br><br>So, stop by her home or look out for her around school. Cateyes is a cool girl worth meeting! Thanks for being a good citizen, Cateyes, and congrats on being named Citizen of the Week!</div>
